# 1. Copy this file and rename to: neon-db.txt
# 2. Paste your Neon connection string on the next line (from neon.tech -> Connect -> Copy)
# 3. Save. Put neon-db.txt on BOTH PCs in the Swallow folder.
# 4. Run run-Lastivka.ps1 - both PCs will use the same database.

